{"tid":634364,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"宜家用7字頭手提電話號碼係罪","createTime":"2018-04-19T07:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T08:55:17.000Z","uid":126399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3810676d2c5d3ea3e0ac8a16ea8ce165ebed6542","tid":634364,"uid":126399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T07:23:18.000Z","msg":"啱啱申請咗個7字頭嘅手提電話號碼，點知真係衝出嚟柒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好多Apps同網站都話個no係 Invalid Phone Number, 就算有啲直頭入完個號碼都收唔到個 Verification Code SMS <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時得 Telegram 係完全無問題，WhatsApp 要搞啲嘢先可以登記到 7字頭號碼，其他個啲直頭無反應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nGoogle, FB, Ig 直頭話係 Invalid Number, 真係唔知要等到幾時先得<br />\n<br />\n唉真係衝出嚟柒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7efd54162b81aa40db40dc1efa41a2f1c3e75794","tid":634364,"uid":170677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T07:23:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6eee66f0902746d95c58133751a29932bd0812b","tid":634364,"uid":165632,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T07:24:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"365d4674b163fb2b40516c454f72bf63b8a3b864","tid":634364,"uid":171020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T07:44:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f04b56cf306acf30f813ab050c8ac501c42b871f","tid":634364,"uid":178352,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T07:58:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb6a524a31d4bf8d0deb3ac7be4f82952688411d","tid":634364,"uid":170386,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T08:25:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91abd0ad0b1f76d9da6abaabaae52e7ea4f75144","tid":634364,"uid":167659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T08:55: